# Input

```scss
$direct:#{$name};
$binary:#{1+2};
$nested:#{($a+1)*2};
$call:#{map-get($map,
key)};
$list:#{1,2,3};

```


# Formatted

```scss
$direct: #{$name};
$binary: #{1 + 2};
$nested: #{($a + 1) * 2};
$call: #{map-get($map, key)};
$list: #{1, 2, 3};

```
